snippet.title: Hangul Attack - Free Korean Typing Game
snippet.description:
There is a newer version (2021) of this game here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IQ0JQ-XC9eg

I made a free Korean Hangul typing game that you can download and play. It's on my web site at gobillykorean.com. You can download it here: https://gobillykorean.com/free-korean-typing-game-hangul-attack-new-update-2021/

This is a completely new version of the game, remade from scratch.

Practice typing with a Korean keyboard and shoot meteors (and powerups) in "Hangul Attack."

If there's enough interest, I can add more features to the game.

Please consider supporting me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/gobillykorean

Want to start learning Korean? Check out my book, "Korean Made Simple" on Amazon: http://amzn.to/2bDBi6h (affiliate)
